# Agents

- Agent/task definitions live in `agents/config/agents.yaml` and `tasks.yaml`.
- Default model string **`gpt-4.1-nano`** unless `OPENAI_MODEL` overrides.
- When adding tools to Trend Hunter, register keys in `tool_sets` and map names in `crew_adapter.py`.
- Sequential process — task order in YAML is authoritative.
